data.description: Welcome to this stunning property that offers the perfect blend of space, functionality, and style. Situated on a generous .50-acre lot, this home boasts a remarkable 2016 sq ft shop with concrete floors, 220 power, providing ample room for all your hobbies and storage needs.Step inside and be greeted by an inviting open concept living area that seamlessly flows into a sunroom, where natural light floods the space through charming French doors. The primary suite is a true oasis, featuring a beautifully tiled shower and granite countertops. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and additional office space, this home offers versatility to accommodate your unique lifestyle. The 22x24 carport provides convenient covered parking. There are blackberry bushes, plum trees, weeping willow & shade trees.
